- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper discusses building models to predict a user's preferred conversational style. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is relevant as the paper is about user preferences and feedback on interactions with a digital assistant. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is possible as the paper may involve techniques for retrieving and analyzing user feedback. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is less likely but still possible as the paper may involve analyzing speech patterns and audio data.
